}
```

This function takes a pointer to a `pcap_t` structure as input and returns the major version number of the pcap library associated with that structure. It first checks if the `pcap_t` structure has been activated. If not, it returns an error code `PCAP_ERROR_NOT_ACTIVATED`. Otherwise, it returns the `version_major` field from the `pcap_t` structure.

